{"tid":1709961,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我讀清水灣道女校...","createTime":"2019-11-12T04:47:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T06:04:39.000Z","uid":209657,"like":10,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c20d663cd6452a9757c283031aa77ce56e422447","tid":1709961,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:47:06.000Z","msg":"我爸爸係一個壞左既人<br />\n尋日佢做咗件好錯嘅事（唔想講）<br />\n但我唔明點解啲人要搞我地兩姊妹...<br />\n仲有人話要攞我啲相黎打飛機<br />\n我知我靚...但係真係好disgusting囉<br />\n班連登仔又矮又柒又毒又窮又肥<br />\n點可以攞我啲靚靚相黎j架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔知以後點返學 點出街...<br />\n就算轉校啲人都認得我...<br />\n照樣會見到我就陰陰嘴笑<br />\n然後返到屋企瘋狂j我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過唔緊要<br />\n我爸爸話我畢業會去美國讀大學<br />\n哼 你班人最多咪淨係去到大灣區<br />\n去美國之後我就可以食洋腸<br />\n諗起都覺得好興奮呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196384174d97698e940db6794550f81eeb2a7257","tid":1709961,"uid":209657,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:48:52.000Z","msg":"你班連登仔 我學校係德望唔望得<br />\n你地唔好再望我啦！！！"},{"pid":"a39b7b083acc4c9c1c18ee798e7da216dec524a0","tid":1709961,"uid":174882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:48:59.000Z","msg":"成班連登仔要姦咗你兩姊妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nget ready<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0170fa4bf09f855bb08888acec760d47f6b391e3","tid":1709961,"uid":178800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:49:53.000Z","msg":"想問下你兩姐妹大個係咪會考警察?"},{"pid":"bb8b62c8990b56729239dfbd86f96be059edc0fb","tid":1709961,"uid":209657,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a39b7b083acc4c9c1c18ee798e7da216dec524a0","tid":1709961,"uid":174882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:48:59.000Z","msg":"成班連登仔要姦咗你兩姊妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nget ready<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig